g.text: + initialize(address _admin_board, string memory _name, string memory _symbol, string memory _server) public initializer
- raw_transfer(address _from, address _to, uint256 _ticket_id, bool _raw) private zero(_from) zero(_to) ticket(_ticket_id) ticket_exists(_ticket_id) owner(_ticket_id, _from)
e Mint(address indexed _issuer, uint256 indexed _ticket_id, address indexed _owner, uint256_price, address _currency)
e Sale(address indexed _issuer, uint256 indexed _ticket_id, address indexed _owner, uint256_end)
e SaleClose(address indexed _issuer, uint256 indexed _ticket_id, address indexed _owner)
e Buy(address indexed _issuer, uint256 indexed _ticket_id, address indexed _new_owner, address _old_owner, uint256 _price, address _currency)
+ mint(address _to, uint256 _price, address _currency) public zero(_to) returns (uint256)
+ openSale(uint256 _ticket_id, uint256 _end) public eventOnly ticket(_ticket_id) ticket_exists(_ticket_id) issuer(_ticket_id)
+ closeSale(uint256 _ticket_id) public eventOnly ticket(_ticket_id) ticket_exists(_ticket_id) issuer(_ticket_id)
+ buy(uint256 _ticket_id, address _buyer, uint256 _price, address _currency) public eventOnly ticket(_ticket_id) ticket_exists(_ticket_id) issuer(_ticket_id) zero(_buyer)
+ ownerOf(uint256 _ticket_id) public view ticket(_ticket_id) ticket_exists(_ticket_id) returns (address _owner)
+ approve(address _approved, uint256 _ticket_id) public ticket(_ticket_id) ticket_exists(_ticket_id) owner(_ticket_id, msg.sender)
+ isApprovedForAll(address _owner, address _operator) public view zero(_owner) zero(_operator) returns bool
+ safeTransferFrom(address _from, address _to, uint256 _ticket_id, bytes memory _data) public
+ tokenURI(uint256 _ticket_id) external view ticket(_ticket_id) ticket_exists(_ticket_id) returns (string memory)
- codeAt(address _addr) internal view returns (bytes memory o_code)
